1. Crear Docker File
    1.1 Ejecutar docker build .

2. Crear compose
    2.1 ejecutar docker-compose build

3. Crear django project  ( docker-compose run app sh -c "django-admin.py startproject app .")

4. To test Unit testing files from django
    4.1 docker-compose run app sh -c "python manage.py test"










# CODIGO UTIL
docker build .
docker-compose build
docker-compose run app sh -c "python manage.py test && flake8"